<TITLE> Bus runs over, kills father, son </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Narsinghdi, July 2 (bdnews24.com)A speeding bus on the Dhaka-Sylhet highway ran over a rickshaw-van driver and his son on Thursday. bdnews24.com Narsinghdi correspondent said Hanif Miah, 40, and his son Soleman, 15, died on the spot as the Dhaka-bound bus rushing at breakneck speed ran over their van at Tataparha near Madhabdi. Hanif and Soleman were travelling to Madhabdi from Panchdona. Narsinghdi police recovered the dead bodies and sent them to the morgue for autopsy. A case has been filed with Narsinghdi Sadar Police Station. 
